n\nThe interconnection application status with the utility company is {{ enrolled_object.interconnection_status }}.\n\nThe construction status is {{ enrolled_object.install_status }}. \n\nThe inspection status is {{ enrolled_object.final_inspection_status }}. ", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "2", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-1", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "1"}, "fields": {"delta": "2", "time_unit": "MINUTES"}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "3", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "4"}, "fields": {"property_name": "permit_status_update___sms", "value": {"staticValue": "Hello, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers. Your project is still in the Permitting & Interconnection phase and is currently under review.\n\nWe submitted your application to {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153777960.record_name }} on {{ enrolled_object.permit_submit_date }}. Based on recent averages, approvals from this agency typically take about {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153777960.permit_turnaround_average }} days. While there\u2019s no new update this week, we\u2019re actively monitoring your project and will notify you as soon as we hear back. Thanks again for your patience!\n\nReply END to stop texts.", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "4", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "6"}, "fields": {"property_name": "permit_status_update___email", "value": {"staticValue": "Hello, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers. Your project is still in the Permitting & Interconnection phase and is currently under review.\n\nWe submitted your application to {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153777960.record_name }} on {{ enrolled_object.permit_submit_date }}. Based on recent averages, approvals from this agenc